{
  "sourceLanguage": "en",
  "strings": {
    "": {},
    "%@ を取り込みました": {
      "comment": "A message that appears in an alert when a .pack file is successfully imported. The argument is the name of the pack.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ has been imported!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "%@ を追加しました。アプリで内容を確認しましょう": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ has been added. Check it in the app."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ad": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "About & User Guide"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "アプリの紹介・取扱説明"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用が可能か確認できません。通信環境をご確認ください。": {
      "comment": "Error message shown to the user when fetching the credit balance from the server fails.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Can’t check if AI features are available right now. Please check your internet connection."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券が不足しています。下のメニューから購入してください。": {
      "comment": "Failure message shown in the UI when the user's AI credit is insufficient.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You’re out of AI tickets! Get more from the menu below."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券が残っている間は購入できません、残りが0枚になってからご購入ください。": {
      "comment": "A message to inform the user that AI purchase is only allowed when the remaining credits are zero.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You still have some AI tickets left! You can buy more once your balance hits zero."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券が購入できませんでした、課金されません。": {
      "comment": "Alert message displayed when purchasing AI credit fails.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Couldn’t buy AI tickets. Don’t worry, you weren’t charged."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券の購入": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Purchase AI Tickets"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券の購入中に問題が発生しました、課金されません。通信環境をご確認ください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We ran into a problem while purchasing AI tickets. You haven’t been charged. Please check your internet connection."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券は端末に安全に保管されますが、端末が壊れたりアプリを削除すると失われます。貯めずに早めにお使いください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your AI tickets are safely kept on this device, but they’ll be lost if you delete the app or your device breaks. Try to use them soon!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券を%lld枚追加しました。": {
      "comment": "Text to be displayed in an alert when a purchase is successful. The argument is the number of additional AI coupons added.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Added %lld AI tickets."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AI利用券残り %lld 枚": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%lld AI tickets remaining"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "app.title": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Packlin"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "モチメモ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "g": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "g"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "group (%lld) [%@]": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "group (%1$lld) [%2$@]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "groupList.footer.description": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "* Tap the group icon to edit its details\n* Tap the row to show the item list\n* Press and hold the row to drag and reorder\n* The group icon status is shown as follows"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "・グループアイコンをタップすると内容を編集\n・行をタップするとアイテム一覧を表示\n・行を長押しするとドラッグして並べ替え\n・グループアイコンの表示状況は下記の通り"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "info.url": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "https://docs.azukid.com/CalcRoll/"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "https://docs.azukid.com/CalcRoll/"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "item (%lld) [%@]": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "item (%1$lld) [%2$@]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "itemList.footer.description": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "* Tap the item icon to toggle the check status\n* Tap the row to open the edit screen\n* Tap the quantity field to edit the amount\n* Press and hold the row to drag and reorder\n* The item icon status is shown as follows"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "・アイテムアイコンをタップするとチェック切り替え\n・行をタップすると編集画面を表示\n・数量箇所をタップすると数量編集\n・行を長押しするとドラッグして並べ替え\n・アイテムアイコンの表示状況は下記の通り"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Key": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Key"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "kg": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "kg"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "OK": {
