    "グループ内の必要なアイテムが全てチェック済み": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Everything you need in this group is checked off!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "グループ名": {
      "comment": "A section header for the group name field.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Group Name"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "この購入はすでに完了しています、枚数を更新しました。": {
      "comment": "Alert message when the same purchase is attempted again, and the number of AI coupons is updated.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This purchase is already complete. We’ve refreshed your ticket count."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "コピーを作成する（複製）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Make a copy (duplicate)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "タップして広告をご覧ください": {
      "comment": "A navigation title that appears at the top of the view, describing its purpose.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap to watch the ad"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チェックと在庫を連動": {
      "comment": "A toggle label that lets the user enable or disable the connection between checking items and their stock levels.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Link checks with inventory"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チェック済み": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Checked"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピー(AI)に作成を依頼": {
      "comment": "A button label that translates to \"Request to create with Chappy (AI).\"",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask Chappy (AI) to create it"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピー(AI)に依頼する": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask Chappy (AI)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピー(AI)に修正を依頼": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask Chappy (AI) to revise it"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピーからの応答がありません": {
      "comment": "Text displayed in a local notification when AI-generated text generation fails. The message provided to the user is truncated for brevity.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No response from Chappy"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピーが忙しそうです。時間をおいて再度お試しください。": {
      "comment": "Error message shown when a request to the server fails with an unexpected error.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chappy seems busy. Please try again later."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピーが考えています。提案が届けば通知しますので、閉じても大丈夫です。他の操作をしてお楽しみください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chappy is thinking. We’ll notify you when suggestions arrive, so feel free to close this and keep exploring."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピーの提案が届きました": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chappy’s suggestion has arrived"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "チャッピーの提案によりパックを更新しました。さらにカスタマイズしてご利用ください。": {
      "comment": "Message shown to the user when a new pack is successfully generated using the AI, and the view is not visible to the user. Instead, a local notification is shown.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The pack has been updated with Chappy’s suggestions. Feel free to customize it further."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "パックが見つかりません": {
